{"tid":2278563,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"商人涉冒警狎14歲女童　還押至周三再訊 (15:36)","createTime":"2020-11-09T08:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T11:59:57.000Z","uid":54337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b04cc6b3ad42c9b83a04b857c8551572e2f10fa7","tid":2278563,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"商人涉冒警狎14歲女童 還押至周三再訊 (15:36)<br />\n<br />\n27歲商人今年8月在網上交友平台結識一名14歲女童後，涉訛稱自己是沙田警區高級督察，並聲稱能替女童解決她男友被捕的問題，帶女童到酒店並侵犯她。商人被控一項冒認公職人員罪及一項非禮罪，今（9日）在西九龍裁判法院提訊，暫無須答辯。案件押後至本周三（11日）再訊，以待警方進行認人手續，被告須還押警方看管。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳柏傑（27歲），報稱商人，被控於今年8月25日在香港某處假冒公職人員，即香港警務處警務人員；以及於今年11月1日，在旺角砵蘭街「維多利亞酒店」内猥褻侵犯女孩X。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，被告自稱是沙田區的高級督察，在網上結識了14歲的X，X在聊天時透露他的男友被捕，被告聲稱可幫助她，其後被告帶X到酒店，要求X替他口交，X就範，最終事件由X的家人揭發。"},{"pid":"6bab99171b0de32868b13c756f5ecefcb9d6ca70","tid":2278563,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201109/s00001/1604904672943/%e5%95%86%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%89%e5%86%92%e8%ad%a6%e7%8b%8e14%e6%ad%b2%e5%a5%b3%e7%ab%a5-%e9%82%84%e6%8a%bc%e8%87%b3%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%89%e5%86%8d%e8%a8%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201109%2Fs00001%2F1604904672943%2F%25e5%2595%2586%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2586%2592%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%258b%258e14%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e7%25ab%25a5-%25e9%2582%2584%25e6%258a%25bc%25e8%2587%25b3%25e5%2591%25a8%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%2586%258d%25e8%25a8%258a&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2Ba0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=39a27074\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201109%2Fs00001%2F1604904672943%2F%25e5%2595%2586%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e6%25b6%2589%25e5%2586%2592%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e7%258b%258e14%25e6%25ad%25b2%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e7%25ab%25a5-%25e9%2582%2584%25e6%258a%25bc%25e8%2587%25b3%25e5%2591%25a8%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%2586%258d%25e8%25a8%258a&h=19a4c376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201109/s00001/1604904672943/%e5%95%86%e4%ba%ba%e6%b6%89%e5%86%92%e8%ad%a6%e7%8b%8e14%e6%ad%b2%e5%a5%b3%e7%ab%a5-%e9%82%84%e6%8a%bc%e8%87%b3%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%89%e5%86%8d%e8%a8%8a</a>"},{"pid":"85b219de38ce6f636610190fa2c1f57ac2eb2844","tid":2278563,"uid":44243,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"男友被捕<br />\n玩交友app<br />\n14歲含撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bd195935b22cbb80e4d4dbee37f13e55aaeb96","tid":2278563,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"屌好撚慘"},{"pid":"fa41894f35bd755dae74d694af1e82e909027887","tid":2278563,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"如果係真警察的話，個官一定會話：熱心公益，貢獻社會，服務國家，所以予以輕判。<br />\n大事化小，小事化無。<br />\n<br />\n假警察囉喎，下場就慘囉。<br />\n<br />\n所以作奸犯科呢，都係留俾有牌爛仔嘅去做啦。<br />\n一般小市民無牌，但偏要做爛仔 = 衰鳩硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b795c5b869d2d3e1d3aa74e4ee10586cca1567","tid":2278563,"uid":254745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"識扮督察<br />\n蠢唔晒"},{"pid":"ad830a135e518edeff03d8656f76cc2a0bf299d4","tid":2278563,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:45:14.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=